description:
Koharu, in her cat Kojiro's body, is captured--first by the art teacher, who forces her to pose, and then by someone who lost their cat in a tragic accident. Will she be able to escape before sundown? Meanwhile, Hanamaru runs into a cute little girl with incredibly good luck. Hanamaru is losing his memory--but only about Nanao! Is Hanamaru doomed to lose his memory of her forever?

description: Northern Plains High newcomer Jeffry Dietz arrives to a mixed reception...  some of his new classmates are friendly, but one nearly forces him into a fight... to be continued, he lets Jeffry know.  Jeffry misses the urban setting of where he moved from, and this small town offers him almost nothing to do on the weekends.  But he's determined to make the best of a less-than-ideal situation.
name: First Day

description:
The Muse is DEAD! Long live the Muse! Or so say the headlines. But like any good reporter sometimes the best news is the news you make happen. For years, the 10th Muse has fought a variety of evil in the name of justice, but she has never battled the media! If the future is written, the Muse is a dead woman and there is nothing the gods can do about it. In the bigger-than-life series finale, Emma Sonnet encounters her final destiny...but will it mean her death? This is a giant-sized 44-page roller coaster ride that will keep fans on the edge of their seat until the very last page!

description: Beginning in Marshville July 10, 1993 11:10 a.m. just 3 minutes before the accident that will propel Marshville back in time, three young researchers are searching for big foot in the Oregon woods. After spotting not just one but a pair of Bigfoots the town and surrounding woods phase into the past the hunters and one of their prey are lost in the prehistoric jungle. The researchers are quickly dealt with by the elements but the 'missing link' fairs a bit better, although confused by the new surroundings, hungry, and fending off attacks from meat eaters. Meanwhile Mariam Cooper, Captain Lavery, and Professor Cook are trying to convince some of the residence to move closer to the center of town for protection but Bucky and Becky Radison and their new baby do not want to leave home. Soon the hunger of the female bigfoot leads her to the home of the Radison's where she is almost shot trying to nab a plate of burgers getting away just in time to run headlong into Klyde.

Prehistoric Pinups is back with another fantastic offering of Budd's sexy Cavewoman! We've seen Budd do some incredible paintings and drawings this past year and we've collected the very best into this new issue of our best selling pinup series! We guarantee not to disappoint as you look at page after page of Meriem, sometimes in various stages of undress, in jungle settings and beyond! Cavewoman fans and new collectors alike are in for a treat with Prehistoric #6!

name: The Travails Of Ms. Nagi Mahori (part 12)

description: Baby Jack-Jack, everyone's favorite superpowered toddler, battles...a nasty cold! Hopefully the rest of the Parr family can stay healthy, because normal denizens of Metroville are starting to exhibit superpowers. Can The Incredibles discover the cause of both outbreaks before the city is left in total shambles?

Yoh and Lyserg are in the heat of battle with Luchist! Will they be able to defeat the X-Laws once and for all so they can finally move on to Hao? More important, if Hao's victory in the Shaman Fight is indeed inevitable, how can Yoh and friends ever hope to defeat him?
name: Cornerstone

description:
The Golem runs out of energy, so Dr. Munzer wants to command it to self-destruct, but Anna wants to keep the Golem as a weapon against Hao. Then Little Opacho shows up, bearing a message that Yoh must return to the Shaman Fight, or Hao will destroy both the Golem and the kids!

description: The Explorers are sent by the President to investigate the disappearance of the town of Marshville. Once at the site where the town once stood, they discover a hole in the fabric of time and are transported back to the distant past where they meet Cavewoman and her friends.

Collecting the acclaimed first five issues of the hot new series! When a case she's lost leads to the murder of innocents, prosecutor Kate Spencer rages into the night, tracking the perp who's eluded justice in the courts. She's found her true calling. She is the Manhunter. And she likes it!
name: Vol. 1

description: Don't miss this new volume collecting MANHUNTER #6-14! Prosecutor Kate Spencer is poised to take on the trial of the year, as the eyes of the nation are on her latest case: finding the Shadow Thief guilty of murdering the hero Firestorm.
name: Vol. 2

description: In a city that can swallow you whole, only one man can find what cannot be found. Ninette Moeller steps off a flight from Paris and onto the mean streets of New York City. She's after one LUCIEN DENALI, a man who has done unspeakable damage to her. She hires the tireless MR. KEEN: Tracer of Lost Persons.

volume.name: Mr. Keen: Tracer of Lost Persons

description: After a visit to the local Brujah, Lucienlays siege on the safehouse Ninette and MR. KEEN are operating out of. The intense violence spills more than BLOOD, as the binds of Ninette's mind come loose in an avalanche of horror, soaking KEEN in the filth of her past.

description: MR. KEEN, NINETTE, and MIKE make their seige against LUCIEN DENALI's horrible sex mansion in this ego-destroying finale! Will Ninette exact her revenge for the crimes Denali commited against her?

volume.name: Mr. Keen: Tracer of Lost Persons

description: One of the most award-winning and acclaimed comics series of the last several years returns to the shelves this September with a perfect new jumping-on point for new readers -- or those who’ve gotten hooked on Brubaker and Phillips hit series INCOGNITO and are craving more! CRIMINAL’s most popular character, TRACY LAWLESS returns in THE SINNERS. It’s been a year since Tracy was forced into working for the bad guys, and now made men are turning up dead all over the city, in what appears to be mob-style hits. But since criminals don’t go to the cops for justice… only Tracy can solve this crime.
name: The Sinners, Part 1
